text: Dianella may refer to: * Dianella (beetle), a species and genus of beetle in the family Carabidae now known as Diamella * Dianella (gastropod), a genus of freshwater snails in the family Hydrobiidae * Dianella (plant), a genus of flowering plants * Dianella, Western Australia, a suburb of Perth, Australia ** Dianella White Eagles, a football club from the suburb
title: Dianella
